{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">认识电路，了解用电器的工作状态。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">串联电路有分压作用。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电源、开关、滑动变阻器、小电机、嗡鸣器、电流表、导线</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.闭合开关</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">S</span><sub>1</sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，观察小电机和嗡鸣器工作状态；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.调整滑动变阻器，观察小电机和嗡鸣器工作状态；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.闭合开关</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">S</span><sub>2</sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，观察小电机和嗡鸣器工作状态；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.调整滑动变阻器，观察小电机和嗡鸣器工作状态。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">只闭合</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">S</span><sub>1</sub>，嗡鸣器工作，小电机不能工作；闭合<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">S</span><sub>1</sub>、<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">S</span><sub>2</sub>，嗡鸣器不能工作，小电机工作。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">发生局部短路时，被短路元件不能正常工作。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}